Amy-Lee de Jager was taken by four men in a white Toyota Fortuner on Monday morning. JOHANNESBURG - Six-year-old Amy-Lee de Jager has been found. She was kidnapped from outside her school in Vanderbijlpark on Monday. REVEALED: Who is kidnapping SA's children and how De Jager was snatched, just as her mother was dropping her off at school. The kidnappers demanded a R2-million ransom for her release. Four men in an unmarked Toyota Fortuner were seen taking the Grade-R pupil.